<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 12:12:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队计划招募没有以色列国防军经验的定居者来保卫极端正统的西岸定居点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-to-recruit-settlers-with-no-army-experience-to-guard-west-bank-settlements/0000018b-8f63-d7a8-afcf-afe3a9b00000</link><description>新兵预计将接受为期三周的加速基础训练，之后他们将武装起来并驻扎在定居点。该计划向 27 岁至 50 岁、未曾在以色列军队服役的平民开放</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 11:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-to-recruit-settlers-with-no-army-experience-to-guard-west-bank-settlements/0000018b-8f63-d7a8-afcf-afe3a9b00000</guid></item><item><title>德国正式取缔哈马斯，解散庆祝 10 月 7 日大屠杀的组织 Samidoun</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/germany-officially-outlaws-hamas-disbands-samidoun-group-that-celebrated-oct-7-massacre/0000018b-8f95-d7a8-afcf-afb749e90000</link><description>德国最高安全官员在宣布禁令的声明中表示，“在德国举行自发的‘庆祝活动’，以回应哈马斯对以色列的可怕恐怖袭击，显示了萨米敦的反犹太主义、不人道的世界观”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 11:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/germany-officially-outlaws-hamas-disbands-samidoun-group-that-celebrated-oct-7-massacre/0000018b-8f95-d7a8-afcf-afb749e90000</guid></item><item><title>检查站、商店关门、药品不足：哈原已成为一座鬼城</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/checkpoints-closed-shops-not-enough-medicine-hawara-has-become-a-ghost-town/0000018b-8abc-dce3-afaf-affe3c450000</link><description>以色列军方设置了路障，将约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦城镇一分为二，使人们难以移动或到达周围社区。由于担心定居者的袭击，居民在离开家时三思而后行。军方表示已命令部队允许自由行人通行</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 10:52:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/checkpoints-closed-shops-not-enough-medicine-hawara-has-become-a-ghost-town/0000018b-8abc-dce3-afaf-affe3c450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府担心卡塔尔人质调解受到损害，不阻止半岛电视台关闭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-prevents-al-jazeera-shut-down-fearing-harm-to-qatari-hostage-mediation/0000018b-8f0e-d728-a9ab-dfde4aff0000</link><description>以色列内阁批准了紧急法规，允许政府关闭安全官员认为危害国家安全的媒体渠道，但通讯部长和司法部长均表示，决定权在国防部长约阿夫·加兰特手中</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 08:46:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-prevents-al-jazeera-shut-down-fearing-harm-to-qatari-hostage-mediation/0000018b-8f0e-d728-a9ab-dfde4aff0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列，当心：在战争中，末日犹太极端民族主义者正处于狂喜状态</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-beware-nationalist-haredis-are-in-a-state-of-ecstasy/0000018b-8c23-d7a8-afcf-aea34fd90000</link><description>他们的眼睛闪闪发光。他们谈论“第二次灾难”。他们相信这是弥赛亚的时代。对于极端正统民族主义者来说，与哈马斯的战争是一个双重幻想：犹太人对大以色列的全面统治，以及从当今自由民主以色列的废墟中诞生的原教旨主义犹太人</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 07:41:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-beware-nationalist-haredis-are-in-a-state-of-ecstasy/0000018b-8c23-d7a8-afcf-aea34fd90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人在约旦河西岸疑似枪击事件中丧生；以色列国防军指挥官在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-live/idf-strikes-in-lebanon-after-missile-launch-hamas-commander-killed-in-idf-airstrike/0000018b-8e75-db7e-af9b-eff7619c0000</link><description>自加沙地面行动开始以来，已有 18 名以色列士兵和军官丧生 ■ 哈马斯：195 名巴勒斯坦人在以色列对贾巴利亚难民营的袭击中丧生 ■ 导弹发射后，以色列国防军在黎巴嫩发动空袭 ■ 以色列空袭杀死了哈马斯贾巴利亚旅指挥官和一名巴勒斯坦人10 月 7 日大屠杀的领导人 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：超过 9,000 名巴勒斯坦人被杀 ■ 242 名人质被扣押在加沙，40 人仍然失踪 ■ 至少 1,300 名平民和士兵在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 05:25:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-live/idf-strikes-in-lebanon-after-missile-launch-hamas-commander-killed-in-idf-airstrike/0000018b-8e75-db7e-af9b-eff7619c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列寻求国际合法性，但时间已经不多了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-seeks-international-legitimacy-but-time-is-running-out/0000018b-8ca8-d46b-a18f-8cf906bf0000</link><description>尽管哈马斯的杀人意图显而易见，但国际合法性的时钟正在滴答作响，以色列对黑色星期六悲剧的同情似乎正在迅速减少</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 04:07:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-seeks-international-legitimacy-but-time-is-running-out/0000018b-8ca8-d46b-a18f-8cf906bf0000</guid></item><item><title>防止西岸战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/preventing-war-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-8c72-db7e-af9b-eff3d04e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 02:12:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/preventing-war-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-8c72-db7e-af9b-eff3d04e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列从加沙撤出战略尚未被采纳</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-exit-strategy-from-gaza-that-hasnt-been-adopted/0000018b-8c23-d46b-a18f-8cfb36d20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 02:09:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-exit-strategy-from-gaza-that-hasnt-been-adopted/0000018b-8c23-d46b-a18f-8cfb36d20000</guid></item><item><title>这些是加沙贾巴利亚难民营遭到轰炸后被救出的儿童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/these-are-the-children-extracted-after-the-bombardment-of-gazas-jabalya-refugee-camp/0000018b-8c23-d46b-a18f-8cfb57690000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 01:44:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/these-are-the-children-extracted-after-the-bombardment-of-gazas-jabalya-refugee-camp/0000018b-8c23-d46b-a18f-8cfb57690000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长：立即向巴勒斯坦当局转移资金；哈马斯指挥官在以色列国防军空袭中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-live/11-israeli-soldiers-killed-as-idf-expands-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-8925-d055-afbf-bba702e90000</link><description>自加沙地面行动开始以来，已有 16 名以色列士兵丧生 ■ 也门胡塞武装发动远程导弹和无人机袭击后，以色列军舰部署在红海作为增援部队 ■ 以色列空袭杀死了哈马斯贾巴利亚旅指挥官和 10 月 7 日大屠杀中的一名领导人易卜拉欣·比亚里 (Ibrahim Biari) ■ 哈马斯卫生部：8,000 多名巴勒斯坦人被杀 ■ 240 名人质在加沙被扣，40 人失踪 ■ 至少 1,300 名平民和士兵在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 00:24:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-live/11-israeli-soldiers-killed-as-idf-expands-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-8925-d055-afbf-bba702e90000</guid></item><item><title>为了应对日益增长的压力，哥伦比亚大学和宾夕法尼亚大学宣布打击反犹太主义的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/responding-to-growing-pressure-columbia-and-penn-announce-plans-to-combat-antisemitism/0000018b-8cb7-db7e-af9b-eff725b10000</link><description>自10月7日哈马斯入侵以色列以来，两所大学一直面临来自犹太教师、学生和校友的压力，要求解决犹太学生的安全问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 22:34:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/responding-to-growing-pressure-columbia-and-penn-announce-plans-to-combat-antisemitism/0000018b-8cb7-db7e-af9b-eff725b10000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列人来说，加沙长期血腥战争的现实正在击中要害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/for-israelis-the-reality-of-a-long-bloody-war-in-gaza-is-hitting-home/0000018b-8bf6-db7e-af9b-ebf78b290000</link><description>加沙战争不会是冲向明确胜利线的冲刺，而是一场漫长而混乱的马拉松。以色列公众希望跑步者的脚不会像不久前那样陷入难处理的泥浆中</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 19:25:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/for-israelis-the-reality-of-a-long-bloody-war-in-gaza-is-hitting-home/0000018b-8bf6-db7e-af9b-ebf78b290000</guid></item><item><title>美国认为巴勒斯坦权力机构是加沙问题的可能解决方案，但以色列正在努力削弱它</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sees-palestinian-authority-as-possible-solution-in-gaza-as-israel-works-to-weaken-it/0000018b-8b8a-db7e-af9b-ebcb50e30000</link><description>尽管由总统马哈茂德·阿巴斯领导的陷入困境的约旦河西岸机构得到了拜登政府的支持，但极右翼的以色列部长们却试图扣留对该机构的资助</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 17:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sees-palestinian-authority-as-possible-solution-in-gaza-as-israel-works-to-weaken-it/0000018b-8b8a-db7e-af9b-ebcb50e30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会极右翼成员兹维·苏科特将担任约旦河西岸小组委员会主席</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-knesset-member-zvi-sukkot-to-head-subcommittee-on-the-west-bank/0000018b-8b93-db71-a7df-ffdfd1ea0000</link><description>住棚节年轻时属于宗教犹太复国主义党，曾因涉嫌参与西岸犹太极端主义活动而成为辛贝特安全部门的目标</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 16:20:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-knesset-member-zvi-sukkot-to-head-subcommittee-on-the-west-bank/0000018b-8b93-db71-a7df-ffdfd1ea0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯官员：我们将重复10月7日的袭击，直到以色列被歼灭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/hamas-official-we-will-repeat-october-7-attacks-until-israel-is-annihilated/0000018b-8b9d-db7e-af9b-ebdfbee90000</link><description>哈马斯官员加齐·哈马德告诉黎巴嫩电视台，以色列的存在是所有暴力和痛苦的根源</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 16:10:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/hamas-official-we-will-repeat-october-7-attacks-until-israel-is-annihilated/0000018b-8b9d-db7e-af9b-ebdfbee90000</guid></item><item><title>数百人参与袭击阿拉伯人和左翼分子，但以色列警方只逮捕了四人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-made-only-four-arrests-despite-hundreds-of-attacks-on-arabs-and-leftists/0000018b-8ad0-dce3-afaf-affa24af0000</link><description>警方发言人表示，尽管许多事件都有警察在场，并且一些事件有视频证据，但“事件仍在继续调查，目的是找出更多嫌疑人”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 14:51:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-made-only-four-arrests-despite-hundreds-of-attacks-on-arabs-and-leftists/0000018b-8ad0-dce3-afaf-affa24af0000</guid></item><item><title>黑暗中的拍摄：《国土报》摄影师也加入了这场战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/shots-in-the-dark-haaretz-photographers-turned-into-war-photojournalists-overnight/0000018b-858b-dd28-a7df-959f95fe0000</link><description>记录以色列-哈马斯战争：我们跟随五位《国土报》摄影师，追求展示战争的恐怖，但并未实际展示它</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 13:43:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/shots-in-the-dark-haaretz-photographers-turned-into-war-photojournalists-overnight/0000018b-858b-dd28-a7df-959f95fe0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙发生重大停电后，广泛的互联网和电话服务已恢复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/widespread-internet-and-phone-services-restored-after-major-outages-in-gaza/0000018b-8a43-d466-a9ab-becbb74a0000</link><description>虽然通讯已开始恢复，但红十字会表示，这种停电扰乱了急救人员的工作，并使平民更难寻求安全。上周末，在以色列的猛烈轰炸中，加沙大部分地区的手机和互联网服务突然消失</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 12:47:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/widespread-internet-and-phone-services-restored-after-major-outages-in-gaza/0000018b-8a43-d466-a9ab-becbb74a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列没有在加沙实施种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-is-not-committing-genocide-in-gaza/0000018b-8785-d055-afbf-b7a75d450000</link><description>关于以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝以报复哈马斯 10 月 7 日大屠杀的说法是一个错误的说法，没有国际法依据。这是一种危险的干扰，更有可能导致加沙、以色列及其他地区更多平民死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 12:22:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-is-not-committing-genocide-in-gaza/0000018b-8785-d055-afbf-b7a75d450000</guid></item></channel></rss>